  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare sensitivity, specificity and accuracy of PET, DW MRI
      and CT separately and combined for the evaluation of treatment response and progression-free
      survival in patients with GIST.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
